title: Mythoklash - 1979-1983 EP [2013]
description:
Mashup remixes of popular american songs from 1979 and 1983.

Tracks 01-10 = 1978 songs
Tracks 11-22 = 1982 songs
Source for track 21 chosen by Pat Myette
Source for track 22 chosen by Emily Reinsdorf
Source for track 23 chosen by Dennis Woodroff

Arranged & mixed by Mythoklash

Artwork by Madame Gilles
www.madamegilles.tumblr.com

Thanks to: Madame Gilles, Dennis Woodroff, Pat Myette, Emily Reinsdorf

Released by Neophile Records
